#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int t; cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {
        int n; cin>>n;
        int count=1;
        for(int i=2;i<=(n/2);i++)
        {
            if(n%i==0)
            count=(count*i)%10000;
        }
        if(count==0)
        cout<<"0000"<<endl;
        else
        cout<<count<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
